name: My Window #5
description:
Sometimes I feel that I need to relax.
Everything is coming to me at the same time,
And we know that it's difficult to deal with all stuff in life only with two hands. 


It may be that I am doubting myself but I just have anxiety. 
One of my dreams is not to fight my head anymore.

Some days everything goes to hell and it may be that we are walking behind it.
